  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN US ON DISCORD</h1><p><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>\"Dumb Fight\"  is a local multiplayer party game(NO SINGLE PLAYER MODE) . Players have to control all kinds of dumb and funny-looking babies to beat off opponents by punch gun for becoming the last big winner!<br><br>Your keyboard can provide up to 4 players, to play with 8 players, you will only need 4 extra controllers. <br>Or you may also play with 8 controllers. <br>(Keyboard controlling Guideline)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/995e5f91fe12b5e151c42896098f73cc.poster.avif?t=1612610870\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/995e5f91fe12b5e151c42896098f73cc.webm?t=1612610870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/995e5f91fe12b5e151c42896098f73cc.mp4?t=1612610870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Supports Remote Play Together</strong></h2><br>All you need is one pack of 《DUMB FIGHT》, friends can play with you remotely.<br>Please look at here for more information<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Super smash battel, non-stop enjoyment from 2-8 players.ヽ(✿ﾟ▽ﾟ)ノ </h2>Having an exciting and happy battle with your buddies diving in a coach in a cozy afternoon.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/1058a3a5e1d75b2c4f24dee8a7f2b10f.poster.avif?t=1612610870\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/1058a3a5e1d75b2c4f24dee8a7f2b10f.webm?t=1612610870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/1058a3a5e1d75b2c4f24dee8a7f2b10f.mp4?t=1612610870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Continue framing others in ghost mode even when you are out.ﾍ(ﾟ∀ﾟﾍ) </h2>As a ghost, eating blocks, possessing others are just a piece of cake.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/be79c3aa47929819bd314523926dcdef.poster.avif?t=1612610870\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/be79c3aa47929819bd314523926dcdef.webm?t=1612610870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/be79c3aa47929819bd314523926dcdef.mp4?t=1612610870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extremely intense stage effect, disaster is nothing special.(⁰▿⁰) </h2>Devastating effect is coming anytime, anywhere, all kinds of object would be destroyed, watch out not get yourself in trouble!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/3385bb731f1127a0f57b7f49e6181a01.poster.avif?t=1612610870\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/3385bb731f1127a0f57b7f49e6181a01.webm?t=1612610870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/3385bb731f1127a0f57b7f49e6181a01.mp4?t=1612610870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Team mode, your skillful friend need to be punished.(ಠ౪ಠ) </h2>What to do with the top player? This game provides free team mode, one v.s a Team is not a dream anymore.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 to 8 players locally (NO SINGLE PLAYER MODE) </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Support 8 controllers and 1 keyboard </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique ghost mode </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Full stage environment destruction </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cute and hilarious characters </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Eazy to control </li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Team competition </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Physics-Based Combat System </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiple game modes </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiple stage theme </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/4de52c1a921ef2dc9a4021eb4ead4bf2.poster.avif?t=1612610870\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/4de52c1a921ef2dc9a4021eb4ead4bf2.webm?t=1612610870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1054720/extras/4de52c1a921ef2dc9a4021eb4ead4bf2.mp4?t=1612610870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
